{
  "stem": "16571.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Like I'll come to you and tell you later about what happened to me at Buchenwald, as I said, when they came at Christmas-- round about Christmas time and called up my number, and-- and took us off and sort of finished up going on this train.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "For a-- I should imagine because of interference with bombing and all that, took anything from 10 to 14 hours till we arrived in this place, which is called, I learned later, Hanover.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there, there was really heavy bombings.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were taken into this bunker.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Into this sort of-- what do you call it now?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Shelter.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Where thousands and thousands of people were rushing down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Right out of the train, they were running down and-- and there was-- as I said, we-- we held on to the-- virtually there's two soldiers and an officer, and we held on to their greatcoats not to get lost.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't even think about or dream about escaping or where-- where you going to go?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What are you going to do?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were just like little [YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Just like little [YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So how long were you in Buchenwald altogether?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in Buchenwald, I reckon, about eight and a half to nine months, which after-- I learned afterwards comparing to some of my friends, had it quite easy, if I may say so.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Good going.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my problem arose when I was taken from this-- in the morning, in the daylight.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We took a local train from Hanover to Belsen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They-- they-- they came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As I said, they came and called out the numbers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I don't know-- I thought obviously just me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But eventually we finished up in a room, and there were 17 of us.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
